{"tid":1313504,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[狗隻角度分析]你有冇良心架?","createTime":"2019-07-13T19:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:51:46.000Z","uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"521a7e2f722d5a6afca6a987d3fca728c1a21cc2","tid":1313504,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:37:47.000Z","msg":"無論係咪真係有講&quot;你有冇良心架?&quot;呢句，都想同大家一齊分析狗隻思維<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗狗隻意思係我救左你，你仲諗住跳橋黎跣我一鑊，你有冇良心架。番到狗竇你就知味道!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令我諗起有狗隻幾五年前fb post過既一張gif圖(見以下youtube link)，gif圖開始係段片既第24秒左右。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Lg2dqFCU67Q&amp;t=24s&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLg2dqFCU67Q%26t%3D24s%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=050e5af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Lg2dqFCU67Q&amp;t=24s&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n佢大概意思係話有外國勢力，佢地雖然傷害少部分人，但擋住左更大既禍害(佢地認為)，點解香港人唔識知恩圖執。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家都應該係一樣咁諗<br />\n&ldquo;香港人唔識知恩圖執，你地有冇良心架？<br />\n你不仁我不義，就打L哂你地班暴徒。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後大家將段片拉番第一秒睇 根本就係個巨人自己整舊滾石出黎危害人間，正一仆街。"},{"pid":"c0012f742eba1e0a0e50e0b588a069293e295dfe","tid":1313504,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"}]}